oster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054380/extras/314c2e5fa2d09dad3e0b850ea7b9564a.poster.avif?t=1763409917\" width=600 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054380/extras/314c2e5fa2d09dad3e0b850ea7b9564a.webm?t=1763409917\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054380/extras/314c2e5fa2d09dad3e0b850ea7b9564a.mp4?t=1763409917\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054380/extras/f85ed4d9fffd18b7a5e8c6a66d0e3290.avif?t=1763409917\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let the <strong>intense hip hop soundscape</strong> and <strong>neon-soaked visuals </strong>assault your senses until they are raw. Every moment is punctuated with a visceral soundtrack from Japanese developer and hip hop group, <strong>DON YASA CREW</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054380/extras/e50396e84293d96f1180ef1b97c99a4d.poster.avif?t=1763409917\" width=598 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054380/extras/e50396e84293d96f1180ef1b97c99a4d.webm?t=1763409917\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054380/extras/e50396e84293d96f1180ef1b97c99a4d.mp4?t=1763409917\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054380/extras/e3f4b92091ed8cceea8f67c3ab85fe33.avif?t=1763409917\" width=600 height=200